  97,5,SELAMUN HIJE HETTA METLA’IL-FEXHRI
  98,1,LEM JEKUNIL-LEDHINE KEFERU MIN ‘EHLIL-KITABI WEL-MUSHRIKINE MUNFEKKINE HETTA TE’TIJEHUMUL-BEJJINETU
  98,2,RESULUN MINEL-LAHI JETLU SUHUFÆN MUTEHHERETEN
  98,3,FIHA KUTUBUN KAJJIMETUN
  98,4,WE MA TEFERREKAL-LEDHINE ‘UTUL-KITABE ‘ILLA MIN BA’DI MA XHA’ET/HUMUL-BEJJINETU
  98,5,WE MA ‘UMIRU ‘ILLA LIJA’BUDU ELLAHE MUHLISINE LEHU ED-DINE HUNEFA’E WE JUKIMU ES-SELÆTE WE JU’UTU EZ-ZEKÆTE WE DHELIKE DINUL-KAJJIMETI
  98,6,‘INNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU MIN ‘EHLIL-KITABI WEL-MUSHRIKINE FI NARI XHEHENNEME HALIDINE FIHA ‘ULA’IKE HUM SHERRUL-BERIJETI
  98,7,‘INNEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI ‘ULA’IKE HUM HAJRUL-BERIJETI
  98,8,XHEZA’UUHUM ‘INDE RABBIHIM XHENNATU ‘ADNIN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU HALIDINE FIHA ‘EBEDÆN REDIJEL-LAHU ‘ANHUM WE REDU ‘ANHU DHALIKE LIMEN HASHIJE REBBEHU
